    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Music Monday - The Janet McGarry Band"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>A unique musical experience, this lively, family-friendly show presents bluegrass, gospel and country music in an acoustic setting, up close and personal with the audience, centred around a single condenser microphone, featuring banjo, mandolin, guitar, and upright bass, with tight three-part harmonies.</p>\n\n<p>For more than two decades, Janet McGarry has stood as a defining voice in bluegrass music, earning acclaim on stages at home and abroad. With thirteen celebrated recordings to her name, her work has consistently garnered awards, industry respect, and a devoted following. </p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
